name: SoS Fight Soap
description:
Handmade in the UK with organic, natural materials. This soap is perfect for all of you who like to get a little dirty... It also works just as good for people who have been grappling with stinky Pete- who hasn't washed his gi in a while..

Rammed full of naturally anti-bacterial goodness to keep you clean after a hard sesh on the mats.

*Please note, this product does not cure infections and will not prevent them on its own. You still need to wash your kit after every use and keep yourself clean.
